This website is issued by Pamplona Capital Management, LLP which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (“FCA”). The Pamplona funds are defined as “Unregulated Collective Investment Schemes” (“UCIS”) and the promotion of a UCIS either within the UK or from the UK is severely restricted by statute. Consequently, this website is only made available to professional clients and eligible counterparties as defined by the FCA and to persons falling within the Financial Services and Markets Act 2000 (Promotion of Collective Investment Schemes) (Exemptions) Order 2001. Other persons who view this website should not rely upon it.





















